On second thought I am going to remove the "_keygen" part of the rcvars so this more closely matches the base names of the same feature.

So it will now be this:

: ${openssh_dsa_enable="YES"}
: ${openssh_dsa_flags=""}
: ${openssh_rsa_enable="YES"}
: ${openssh_rsa_flags=""}
: ${openssh_ecdsa_enable="YES"}
: ${openssh_ecdsa_flags=""}
: ${openssh_ed25519_enable="YES"}
: ${openssh_ed25519_flags=""}
